jennom hennes \u00f8yne f\u00e5r historien en troverdighet som isner i blod\u00e5rene. Tittelen p\u00e5 romanen, \"Velkommen til Amerika\", viser moren i en rolle p\u00e5 scenen som en fallen, skallet frihetsgudinne uten fakkel og med speilsk\u00e5r stukket inn i pannen. Kanskje det sanne bildet p\u00e5 en mor som ikke kan v\u00e6re en mor for sine barn.", "LES OGS\u00c5:  Karl Ove Knausg\u00e5rd og hans svenske forfatterkone Linda Bostr\u00f6m Knausg\u00e5rd skal skilles."]}, {"field": "category0", "value": "pluss"}, {"field": "category1", "value": "pluss|kultur"}, {"field": "contenthash", "value": "8451d1e91bab90583bfffeb35beed4945bbdd916c9ee158e583bc1279f34cbb5"}, {"field": "createtime", "value": "2017-01-20T09:41:05.000Z"}, {"field": "description", "value": "Rystende historie om en familie i forfall, der 11-\u00e5rige Ellen reagerer med \u00e5 slutte \u00e5 snakke."}, {"field": "dominantimage", "value": "http://www.adressa.no/incoming/article14084298.ece/qet6jt/ALTERNATES/w980-default/Innbundet.jpg"}, {"field": "dominantimagedimensions", "value": "980x551"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnail", "value": "http://content-thumbnail.cxpublic.com/content/dominantthumbnail/361017385ca06cfe935d051cc6a7b1471b74fa0b.jpg?59525ca1"}, {"field": "dominantthumbnaildimensions", "value": "300x169"}, {"field": "heading", "value": "Sterkt jenteportrett -adressa.no"}, {"field": "id", "value": "361017385ca06cfe935d051cc6a7b1471b74fa0b"}, {"field": "keyword", "value": ["b\u00f8ker", "Vi anmelder bok"]}, {"field": "keywords", "value": "b\u00f8ker,Vi anmelder bok"}, {"field": "kw-category", "value": ["pluss", "kultur"]}, {"field": "kw-classification", "value": "arts-and-entertainment"}, {"field": "kw-concept", "value": ["mor", "familie"]}, {"field": "kw-entity", "value": ["ellen", "dramaten", "gud"]}, {"field": "kw-location", "value": ["stockholm", "amerika"]}, {"field": "kw-pageclass", "value": "article"}, {"field": "kw-person", "value": ["karl ove knausg\u00e5rd", "linda bostr\u00f6m knau